docs.description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of condominiums within the metropolitan of Charleston, SC. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
docs.name: Zillow Home Value Index (Metro Areas): Condominiums - Charleston, SC

docs.description: The Zillow Home Value Index is Zillow's estimate of the median market value of all homes within the county of Albemarle, VA. This number is derived by taking the estimated home value for each home and dividing it by the home's square footage. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
docs.name: Zillow Home Value Index (Counties): Median Value Per Sq. Ft. (All Homes) - Albemarle, VA
